                            Table "public.notifications"
    Column    |           Type           | Collation | Nullable |      Default      
--------------+--------------------------+-----------+----------+-------------------
 id           | uuid                     |           | not null | gen_random_uuid()
 user_id      | uuid                     |           | not null | 
 type         | text                     |           | not null | 
 content      | text                     |           | not null | 
 read         | boolean                  |           |          | false
 created_at   | timestamp with time zone |           |          | now()
 challenge_id | integer                  |           |          | 
Indexes:
    "notifications_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "idx_notifications_challenge_id" btree (challenge_id)
    "idx_notifications_user_id" btree (user_id)
Foreign-key constraints:
    "notifications_user_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
Policies:
    POLICY "Notifications are viewable by the user" FOR SELECT
      USING ((auth.uid() = user_id))

